collection.description:
"We are the ghosts, your nightmare, your daydream."

Weirdo Ghost Gang is a collection of 5555 Lil Ghosts roaming in the web3 playground together with countless frens. Lil Ghosts are not just avatars, but also the duke of a castle, the manager of a street brand, a super rapper, a virtual idol, and the protagonist of an adventure ........ only the boundary of imagination can limit our pace, our existence is not only in the metaverse but will eventually penetrate the reality.
